      "parameters": {
        "content": "MW-00 Router\n\nPurpose\nCentral orchestration workflow.\n\nResponsibilities\n\n• Receive inbound messages\n• Validate requests\n• Normalize payloads\n• Load conversation memory\n• Prevent duplicate processing\n• Invoke AI Receptionist\n• Dispatch responses\n\nSub-workflows\n\nSW-01 Conversation Memory\nSW-02 AI Receptionist\nSW-05 Reply Dispatcher",
